        "special_abilities": [
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "While a battleflower master is fighting in front of two or more noncombatants, whenever they successfully grapple an opponent or hit an opponent with a weapon with the Profession (dancer) weapon special property, they can attempt a Profession (dancer) check with the same DC as a check to demoralize that enemy (as the Intimidate skill) as a swift action. If the grapple attempt or attack roll is a natural 20, the battleflower master can roll twice on the demoralize attempt and take the higher roll. This is an emotion and fear effect.",
                "name": "Working the Crowd",
